description: Above the Sparkling City lights of Seattle, enjoy floor to ceiling views of snowy mountaintops and the Bellevue Skyline 8 miles away. This lovely Southeast corner home features all the amenity one would expect above Seattle's premier Hyatt Hotel; unique access to 5-Star hotel amenities: 24-hour concierge, room service, Gym, sauna, steam room, saline lap pool & spa. Residents-only club features a BBQ terrace, dog lounge, grooming station and event room. Uniquely remodeled with a spacious chef's kitchen and extra storage space. Walk to shopping, theaters, restaurants, Amazon, Google, Apple and Meta, Whole Foods. Easy access to I-5, light rail & SLU streetcar. The veritable foodie paradise of Capitol Hill or Pike Place Market at your doorstep.
